             <!-- \label{eq:LimProd3} -->
             \underbrace{f(x)\cdot g(x) - L_g\cdot L_f}_{\Gamma(x)} = \underbrace{\left[f(x)\cdot g(x)-f(x)\cdot
                 L_g\right]}_{\alpha(x)}+\underbrace{\left[f(x)\cdot L_g - L_f\cdot
